dct_description_sm: "The part colored red shews the extent of the proposed proprietary government."
In upper right margin: Correspondence relative to a grant of a proprietary government to the New Zealand Company.
Publisher's no. from its catalog of nineteenth century maps of New Zealand from the British Parliamentary papers: 11.
